uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T16:17:09.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=9a4fa475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"6cb21e891963d2573ae467e2840e09959d9ba202","tid":1060744,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9681c0d82a068a34a2c81abf1830dc89ae4b588f","tid":1060744,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"放星期六爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T16:22:08.000Z","msg":"終於放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f854104a69eda05d9ae6500428e26bc634e8d4e6","tid":1060744,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cb21e891963d2573ae467e2840e09959d9ba202","tid":1060744,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9681c0d82a068a34a2c81abf1830dc89ae4b588f","tid":1060744,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"放星期六爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/p